{
  "stem": "13471.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, here comes a shell, and it was still headed at me-- they were still after me-- but it landed about 75 yards short.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In other words, at broadside.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We were like this, and over there-- about 75 yards.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Then I thought, holy cow, that's probably an accident.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because the Navy was supposed to have silenced all the shore bomb-- shore artillery on Tinian, but apparently, this one they had overlooked or something.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The next thing I know, there's a explosion on the opposite side of me, about 100 yards out.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know what that means?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If you know anything about artillery, this is a bracket, and I'm right in the middle.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So all the cannoneer has got to do is split the difference, and whack-o, I'm going to catch it the next time, see?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Fortunately, there was about a three-minute interval between the two shots.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were having difficulty, apparently, getting the shots out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Apparently bombardment had damaged the gun, but hadn't completely knocked it out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I told the boys, drop the-- I mean, slip the hook, which means let the chain go, let it go overboard.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But put a buoy on it, you see.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I started and backed out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were also headquarters for a whole bunch of these stranded boat crews whose ships had gone away and left them.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They would come and tie up astern of us, and come on board, and get something to eat, and a cup of coffee.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I'm backing up, and all these boat crews trying to get out of the way.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And as I backed away, I could see the swirl in the water where my propellers had started to grab the water.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
